306
00:19:18,225 --> 00:19:20,627
žao mi je.

307
00:19:20,660 --> 00:19:21,428
A vaša majka?

308
00:19:21,461 --> 00:19:23,863
Pobegla je kada sam bila dete.

309
00:19:23,896 --> 00:19:27,534
