00:26:44,136 --> 00:26:46,138

437
00:26:47,039 --> 00:26:51,644
Obično ne pravim istu grešku dvaput.             

438
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:44,063
Gđice Bentley, pridružite nam se.                 

439
